{"article_id":"NijZ7Fn9lbHdhM1O","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The US attorney general has defended his handling of the Russia inquiry amid complaints","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he misrepresented the special counsel 's findings .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"William Barr was grilled about his decision","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to clear the president of obstruction of justice","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"while appearing before a Senate panel .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"His testimony came after revelations","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that Mr Mueller expressed frustration over the summary of the report .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Mr Mueller is expected to testify to Congress later this month .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"The attorney general , the nation 's top legal official , testified for the first time on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"since releasing Special Counsel Robert Mueller 's 448-page report ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"which found","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"there was no collusion between Russia and President Donald Trump 's campaign in the 2016 election .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"But the report did not exonerate the president of obstruction of justice in his alleged attempts","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"to undermine Special Counsel Mueller .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Mr Barr ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"who was appointed by Mr Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"told the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"he was `` frankly surprised ''","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Mr Mueller did not reach a conclusion","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"on whether the president had tried to obstruct justice .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"He added","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that he was `` absolutely '' confident in his own judgment","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that Mr Trump did not unlawfully attempt to impede the investigation .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"`` I think","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"if he felt","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"that he should n't go down the path","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"of making a traditional prosecutorial decision ,","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"then he should n't have investigated , ''","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"The attorney general 's testimony to Congress came after a letter","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"he received from Mr Mueller","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"was made public ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"in which the special counsel said","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Mr Barr 's summary `` did not fully capture the context , nature and substance '' of his report 's findings ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"and caused `` public confusion about critical aspects of the results of our investigation '' .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"The letter ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"dated 27 March ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"expressed Mr Mueller 's frustration","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that Mr Barr did not release the executive summaries","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"prepared by the special counsel 's team .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Mr Mueller said","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"he shared these concerns two days earlier .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"During the hearing , Mr Barr said","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"that Mr Mueller was not concerned with the accuracy of the summary","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"but with how it was being reported by media .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"`` My understanding was his concern was not the accuracy of the statement of the findings in my letter ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"but that he wanted more out there","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to provide additional context","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"to explain his reasoning","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and why he did n't reach a decision on obstruction , ''","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Mr Barr argued","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that the objections to his summary should be nullified by the release of the report itself ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"calling the controversy","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"surrounding the summary ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"and the consequent hearings ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"`` mind-bendingly bizarre '' .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"`` I made clear from the beginning","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that I was putting out the report , as much of the report","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"as I could ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"and it was clear it was going to take three weeks or so , maybe four , to do that , ''","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Mr Barr said .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"William Barr is a veteran Washington lawyer .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"In Senate testimony on Wednesday , he sounded like one .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"When Democrats grilled the attorney general on his handling of the Mueller investigation ,","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"his answers were carefully parsed and narrowly focused .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"He disputed","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that he misled Congress last month","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"when he said","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"he did n't know about the Mueller team 's dissatisfaction with his four-page letter","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"summarising the concluded Russia inquiry .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"That unhappiness ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"was over media portrayal of the letter , not the letter itself .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"And besides , he was talking to Mr Mueller himself , not his `` team '' .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Then there were the specific instances of possible obstruction","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Mr Mueller highlighted in the report","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"- which","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Mr Barr concluded","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"did n't constitute a crime .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"He had an explanation for them all .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Did Mr Trump instruct Don McGahn to fire Mr Mueller and lie about it ?","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"No ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"Mr Barr said ,","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"the president told his former White House counsel to suggest","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"that Mr Mueller be `` replaced ''","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"because of a conflict of interest -","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"and then write a memo","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"to correct inaccurate media reports .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"And on it went .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Democrats will view this as an attorney general","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"protecting his presidential boss .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Republicans will see it as the nation 's top lawyer","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"defending the rule of law .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"This sets the stage for the day","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"- perhaps soon -","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"when Mr Mueller himself will testify to Congress .","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"It 's one thing to hear what Mr Barr thinks of the Mueller investigation 's conclusions .","depth":4},{"id":99,"text":"The main event will be when Mr Mueller explains it for himself .","depth":4},{"id":100,"text":"Attorney General Barr also blamed Mr Mueller","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"for delaying the report 's full release .","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Mr Mueller 's team declined to flag sensitive material ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"as he requested ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"creating more work for the justice department","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"to redact grand jury material .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"In response to questions from Senator Richard Blumenthal , Mr Barr said","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"he `` did not exonerate '' Mr Trump in his summary or subsequent public statements","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"- directly contradicting the stance of the White House .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"`` I said","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"that we did not believe","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"that there was sufficient evidence","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"to establish an obstruction offence , ''","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Ahead of the hearing , Mr Trump issued as series of tweets ,","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"again asserting his innocence .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"Later ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"when pressed by Mr Blumenthal again ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"Mr Barr referred to Mr Mueller 's letter as `` a bit snitty '' ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and suggested","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"it was not penned by the special counsel himself .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"`` I suspect","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"it was written by a member of his staff , ''","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"Mr Barr said .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"During a heated exchange with Democratic Senator Sheldon Whitehouse , Mr Barr argued","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"that Mr Mueller 's concerns","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"about releasing his executive summaries","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"did not matter","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"as the special counsel was acting as a US attorney under his authority .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"After Mr Mueller submitted the report ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"`` it was my baby '' ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"Mr Barr said .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Republican Senator Charles Grassley asked Mr Barr","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"whether the justice department planned to look into allegations of improper surveillance of Mr Trump 's presidential campaign before the 2016 election .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Mr Barr revealed","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"that he has asked some of his staff to investigate those allegations of `` spying '' ,","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"that he would report any conclusions to Congress .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"Democratic presidential hopeful Senator Kamala Harris pressed Mr Barr on whether he personally reviewed the special counsel 's `` great deal of evidence ''","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"before reaching a conclusion","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"on whether the president obstructed justice .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"The attorney general responded","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"`` no '' ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"he `` accepted the statements in the report as factual record '' .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Senator Harris joined a chorus of Democrats","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"who have called on Mr Barr to resign .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"Mr Barr also said","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"he would not recuse himself from ongoing investigations","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"drawn from the Mueller report .","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"In a tweet , White House press secretary Sarah Sanders tweeted","depth":5},{"id":152,"text":"that Mr Barr had served the president `` honourably '' .","depth":5},{"id":153,"text":"`` Democrats only disgrace and humiliate themselves with their baseless attacks , ''","depth":5},{"id":154,"text":"she posted .","depth":5},{"id":155,"text":"Mr Barr meanwhile cancelled his scheduled Thursday testimony before the Democratic-led House Judiciary Committee .","depth":4},{"id":156,"text":"He had previously objected to a plan","depth":5},{"id":157,"text":"for lawyers to ask questions at the hearing .","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"House Judiciary Chairman Jerry Nadler has threatened to subpoena Mr Barr","depth":4},{"id":159,"text":"if he refused to appear before his panel .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":319,"left":259,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":222,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":167,"right":221,"rel